{"tid":829792,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個世界實在太撚差","createTime":"2018-09-20T16:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T09:20:28.000Z","uid":139907,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ce7bc2b8a33eeed848063e6c00d90e52f9c03f9a","tid":829792,"uid":139907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:56:40.000Z","msg":"就快逼死自己<br />\n好孤獨<br />\n想要既就得唔到<br />\n所以與人相處既快樂都好短促<br />\n打份工其實都係賣時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多野都只係為做而為<br />\n食煙飲酒去旅行去合群 都係唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n放假一停下所有活動 就唔知做乜好<br />\n唔停 又覺得好折墜 好折磨<br />\n望住時間流失 望住自己愈黎愈憔悴<br />\n其實究竟我做緊乜<br />\n究竟其他人又係做緊乜<br />\n為左咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有錢無聊 窮又無聊<br />\n真係好無聊"},{"pid":"2c895207c434ea4d672b12aed3e60a3873ea9571","tid":829792,"uid":10084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:57:27.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"53346493ed24d365c0b1726447845276a77869d0","tid":829792,"uid":139907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2c895207c434ea4d672b12aed3e60a3873ea9571","tid":829792,"uid":10084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:57:27.000Z","msg":"啱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:57:54.000Z","msg":"又準備抱住痛苦入睡"},{"pid":"277a090fbdace919bedc06ea4177edd3fbc9b242","tid":829792,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:58:29.000Z","msg":"得閒上嚟叫春"},{"pid":"17595afb7ac988fd6a71df34b5e4ef9cf1c96377","tid":829792,"uid":10084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"53346493ed24d365c0b1726447845276a77869d0","tid":829792,"uid":139907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2c895207c434ea4d672b12aed3e60a3873ea9571","tid":829792,"uid":10084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:57:27.000Z","msg":"啱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:57:54.000Z","msg":"又準備抱住痛苦入睡"},"citedBy":1,